ED_Title: Observer status for the Ramsar Convention on Wetlands Secretariat in the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText: At its 51st plenary meeting, on 18 December 2019, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Sixth Committee,  decided to defer a decision on the request for observer status for the Ramsar Convention on Wetlands Secretariat in the Assembly  until the seventy-fifth session of the Assembly.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/74/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
